        "body": "<p>extracting from comments(duffymo's and mine)<\/p>\n\n<ol>\n<li><p>Pick a unique <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_package\" rel=\"nofollow\">top-level<\/a> package name.  Example will be<br>\n<code>com.yourcompany<\/code> or <code>com.productname<\/code>... etc<\/p><\/li>\n<li><p>In the exception handling routine, check if the package starts with \nyour pattern.<\/p><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
